{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Ky8e7Lod9EwLsDaHNRjwLv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01RiCPXPw84gpnkHjyottwQr","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/tmp/fdb-11a-pyo3-binding-20260516T174849Z/dev/design/errors.md","old_string":"| `EmbedderDimensionMismatchError` | `EmbedderDimensionMismatchError` | `EmbedderDimensionMismatchError` | open/runtime mismatch |\n\nDecision note:","new_string":"| `EmbedderDimensionMismatchError` | `EmbedderDimensionMismatchError` | `EmbedderDimensionMismatchError` | open/runtime mismatch |\n| `EngineError::EmbedderNotConfigured` | `EmbedderNotConfiguredError`     | `EmbedderNotConfiguredError`     | runtime failure       |\n| `EngineError::KindNotVectorIndexed`  | `KindNotVectorIndexedError`      | `KindNotVectorIndexedError`      | runtime failure       |\n\n2026-05-16 amendment: `EmbedderNotConfigured` and `KindNotVectorIndexed` leaf\nclasses added per Phase 11a codex reviewer finding #3. Python and TS bindings\nexpose them as distinct leaves; both descend from the single rooted base\n(`EmbedderNotConfiguredError` ← `EmbedderError` ← `EngineError`;\n`KindNotVectorIndexedError` ← `VectorError` ← `EngineError`).\n\nDecision note:"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":286,"cache_read_input_tokens":67935,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":286},"output_tokens":58,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9bf016af-3b87-4a97-9dc2-e8a2161a09cc","uuid":"814da433-06b8-4e36-a649-378d45863ac6"}
