{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01TSYps6xjQ4wTjn9wz5Ja5a","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01L2vE6QDskAq8K21oacp3h7","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git add dev/design/errors.md src/python/fathomdb/_fathomdb.pyi src/python/fathomdb/errors.py src/python/pyproject.toml src/python/tests/ src/rust/crates/fathomdb-py/ && git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nfix(11a): reviewer remediation — PanicException, release-safe test hook, leaf classes\n\nAddresses codex `gpt-5.4` BLOCK verdict on Phase 11a (review\n2026-05-16T184507Z). Four findings:\n\n1. (must-fix) Engine panic now raises `pyo3_runtime.PanicException`\n   instead of `EngineError`. Panic is a contract bug, not a typed\n   engine outcome; callers catching `EngineError` must not swallow it.\n   `test_panic_surfaces_as_python_exception` asserts the exact type\n   and that PanicException is NOT an `EngineError` subclass.\n\n2. (must-fix) `fathomdb-py` default features no longer include\n   `test-hooks`; release wheels built via `maturin build --release`\n   (no overrides) ship without `force_panic_for_test`. Editable dev\n   installs (`pip install -e src/python/`) still get the hook because\n   `[tool.maturin] features` opts in. Production wheel CI must build\n   with an explicit `--features` override that omits `test-hooks` —\n   when the release wheel job lands (later 0.6.x slice) it must pass\n   `--features pyo3/extension-module` (no `test-hooks`).\n\n3. (must-fix) Distinct Python leaf classes for two engine variants:\n   `EmbedderNotConfigured` → `EmbedderNotConfiguredError` (under\n   `EmbedderError`), and `KindNotVectorIndexed` →\n   `KindNotVectorIndexedError` (under `VectorError`). Single-rooted\n   hierarchy preserved. `dev/design/errors.md` § Binding-facing class\n   matrix extended with two rows plus 2026-05-16 amendment note; TS\n   stems pre-named so Phase 11b napi-rs has nothing to invent.\n\n4. (should-fix) `test_surface.py` module docstring cites\n   `AC-057a (REQ-053): five-verb runtime SDK surface`.\nEOF\n)\"","description":"commit fixes"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":648,"cache_read_input_tokens":72692,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":648},"output_tokens":61,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9bf016af-3b87-4a97-9dc2-e8a2161a09cc","uuid":"6fb35b83-834e-4312-9805-7b5a7038fc4a"}
